OL,3,CPolice officer cleared of causing
OL,4,Cdeath by dangerous driving
OL,6,FA Greater Manchester Police Officer
OL,7,Fhas been cleared by a jury of causing
OL,8,Fdeath by dangerous driving and death
OL,9,Fby careless driving, following a trial
OL,10,Fat Chester Crown Court.
OL,12,FPC Mark Burrows, 46 from Reddish,
OL,13,FStockport, pleaded not guilty to
OL,14,Fcausing the death of Heather Smedley,
OL,15,F53, following a crash in Oldham.
OL,17,FMrs Smedley, died at the scene of the
OL,18,Fcrash - at Oldham Road's junction with
OL,19,FOtmoor Way in Royton - in December,
OL,20,F2022.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
