PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778238120
OL,3,CPolice officer cleared of causing
OL,4,Cdeath by dangerous driving
OL,6,FPC Burrows, was in pursuit of a
OL,7,Fsuspected stolen Audi A3 at the time,
OL,8,Fin a 'high-powered', unmarked
OL,9,FVolkswagen Golf R and was a member of
OL,10,FGMP's Tactical Vehicle Intercept Unit.
OL,11,FHe activated his emergency lights and
OL,12,Fsirens during the pursuit, the court
OL,13,Fheard.
OL,15,FMrs Smedley was 'making her way home'
OL,16,Fat the time and was turning right in a
OL,17,FPeugeot 108 off Oldham Road into
OL,18,FOtmoor Way at the time of the crash
OL,19,Fhaving used her indicators.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778238120
OL,3,CPolice officer cleared of causing
OL,4,Cdeath by dangerous driving
OL,6,FIn July 2023, Marcel Doyle, the driver
OL,7,Fof the stolen Audi, was jailed for 14
OL,8,Fyears and 11 months after he admitted
OL,9,Fcausing death by dangerous driving.
OL,11,FThe officer in Greater Manchester
OL,12,FPolice's tactical vehicle intercept
OL,13,Funit was charged with the same offence
OL,14,Ffollowing an investigation by the
OL,15,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,16,F(IOPC).
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
