OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778238120
OL,3,CPolice officer cleared of causing
OL,4,Cdeath by dangerous driving
OL,6,FFollowing the verdicts, Assistant
OL,7,FChief Constable of Greater Manchester
OL,8,FPolice Chris Sykes said: "Mark Burrows
OL,9,Fwent to work that day like any other
OL,10,Fday ` intent on serving the public and
OL,11,Fkeeping them safe from those who seek
OL,12,Fto do harm.
OL,14,F"It is nothing short of tragic that an
OL,15,Finnocent woman died in the course of
OL,16,Fthose duties. My thoughts are with
OL,17,FHeather Smedley's loved ones who
OL,18,Fcontinue to mourn her devastating loss.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778238120
OL,3,CPolice officer cleared of causing
OL,4,Cdeath by dangerous driving
OL,6,F"Only one man was responsible for
OL,7,FHeather's death that day and he's
OL,8,Falready behind bars.
OL,10,F"The impact of this incident on Pc
OL,11,FBurrows is lifelong and has been
OL,12,Fcompounded by a criminal
OL,13,Finvestigation. It is important
OL,14,Fofficers are held to account for their
OL,15,Factions, but are not fearful of the
OL,16,Fconsequences of putting themselves in
OL,17,Fharm's way.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
