OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778238120
OL,3,CPolice officer cleared of causing
OL,4,Cdeath by dangerous driving
OL,6,F"Our highly trained pursuit drivers
OL,7,Fare some of the thousands of brave and
OL,8,Fskilled officers who routinely face
OL,9,Fdangerous and difficult situations to
OL,10,Fprotect the public. They have my full
OL,11,Fsupport in continuing to use their
OL,12,Fspecialist training to confront danger
OL,13,Fand keep you safe."
OL,15,FFollowing her death, Mrs Smedley's
OL,16,Ffamily paid tribute to "the most kind,
OL,17,Fgentle, beautiful soul inside and out".
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@SO]xD@XOUyD@fO]
